about this point system right now.  With a point sytem, there will be no rolls and you wont need to bank your points because once you get them for attending a raid, they will be yours until you spend them.  The only situation in which there will be a roll is if two people want to buy the same item, in which case the winner of the roll spends their points and the other person retains them.  The time zone issue can be resolved by setting a time one must be on a raid to receive full points, so those who come an hour or two late but stay 3 or 4 hours will still get full points, and those who can only stay 2 hours or so will recieve partial points.  I tried to push for the system that Talowen suggested but it was determined to be too biased so I started on the point system idea after some people suggested it.  Keep the input coming here, hopefully the system will be out soon.<br>
